<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7920] Thers is a xss issue in schema-browser page of Admin Web UI.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7920</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Open Solr Admin Web UI, select a core(such as collection1) and then click &quot;schema-browse&quot;,and input a url like &quot;http://127.0.0.1:8983/solr/#/collection1/schema-browser?field=cat=&amp;lt;img src=1 onerror=alert(1);&amp;gt;&quot; to the browser address, you will get alert box with &quot;1&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I changed follow code to void this problem:&lt;br/&gt;
Original code:&lt;br/&gt;
 $( &apos;option&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;value=&amp;quot;&amp;#39; + params.route_params.path + &amp;#39;&amp;quot;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&apos;, related_select_element )&lt;br/&gt;
        .attr( &apos;selected&apos;, &apos;selected&apos; );&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Changed code:&lt;br/&gt;
 $( &apos;option&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;value=&amp;quot;&amp;#39; + params.route_params.path.esc() + &amp;#39;&amp;quot;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&apos;, related_select_element )&lt;br/&gt;
        .attr( &apos;selected&apos;, &apos;selected&apos; );&lt;/p&gt;</description>
